Package civitas.celestis.math.matrix

Class LongMatrix

java.lang.Object
civitas.celestis.math.matrix.LongMatrix
All Implemented Interfaces:
Matrix<Long,LongMatrix>, Numeric, Grid<Long,LongMatrix>, Serializable, Iterable<Long>
public class LongMatrix extends Object implements Matrix<Long,LongMatrix>
A matrix of longs. This matrix can be used to store any value which can be packed into 64 bits.
